tathāgatāśvāsānande cācāryatā gambhīrotpattyā vajradharāśvāsānadne cotpannena | caturmudrāpakṣe ca pariniṣpannenācāryatvena karmudrā boddhavyā ||

<commentary>nanu ṣaṇṇāṃ kalaśābhiṣekatāpy uktā sarvatra kalaśavyāpārāt | sā tarhi katham | kalaśaśabdasya payodharopalakṣaṇatvena payodharavyāpārād atrāpi sā ghaṭate | tad etat sarvaṃ darśayati—hastetyādi | gatārtham ||</commentary>
